<div class="comment-quotable" id="commentText_21867" style="position: relative;" data-commentid="21867">
<div><div><p>I believe Iridium will be hosting VDES, which will be an "open" protocol for communications.&nbsp; See&nbsp;<a href="https://www.iala-aism.org/technical/connectivity/vdes-vhf-data-exchange-system/" target="_blank">https://www.iala-aism.org/technical/connectivity/vdes-vhf-data-exchange-system/</a>&nbsp;for info.&nbsp; It provides low power surface to sat to surface communications using just VHF.&nbsp; This would be amazing to build a network on!</p></div><br>
